{
  "stem": "25423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I was still hanging around the city for a while and observing the situation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came to conclusion that I have to get out, and I want to Rawa Ruska.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rawa Ruska was a strange city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a sea of the local administration of the districts, which means the court, schools, police, under the Poles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jewish community, primarily Jew-- maybe 80% of the population was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a service town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's livelihood was strange, because they were importing scraps of furs from Leipzig, which was a very important fur center.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was fashionable in central Europe, and to some extent western Europe, too, for women to wear the lamb's coat, lamb's fur coat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, the scraps as you cut the skins were packed into huge sacks, were sent to this town, and there the Jews were sitting and sewing it together into units which were shipped back to Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is the way they were eking out a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, how far is Rawa Ruska from Lwow?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 50 miles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went there with a cousin of my mother, and we were there-- we got ourselves a job as collectors of rags, scrap metal, and it was a subsidiary of Goering's workers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hermann Goering created an industrial empire for himself in Germany, and Austria, and Czechoslovakia and, in addition to that, there were subsidiaries.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of these civilian Germans was running a subsidiary, which was collecting rags, glass, scrap iron.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Rawa Ruska?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in the office, which means there was a little office, and there I had my little corner, and at night I had two blankets, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Rawa Ruska.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, just in the city, center of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A tiny little office.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
